Colab Dog provides helpful Colab utilities such as:
- Persistent Colab Playlists
- directing straight from GitHub to Google Colab

For far too long, Colab has been building hidden gems without improving their UX and it's time to change that. The goal of Colab Dog is to accelerate data science productivity when working with Colab. Feature requests are always welcome! 

Find out more from https://colabdog.com
